1
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:53,200
Slash

2
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:57,359
Wait

3
00:01:04,799 --> 00:01:06,079
The Qixi Star Diagram Token

4
00:01:06,079 --> 00:01:07,040
Why is it on you?

5
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:08,879
I don't know why that token

6
00:01:08,879 --> 00:01:10,159
is with me either

7
00:01:10,159 --> 00:01:11,159
All I know is

8
00:01:11,560 --> 00:01:13,000
You can't kill me yet

9
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:14,200
Why can't we kill you?

10
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:17,439
The Qixi Star Diagram is a national treasure of Qingyun Kingdom

11
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,640
If anything happens to it

12
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:21,799
It's not something you or I can bear the consequences of

13
00:01:23,120 --> 00:01:23,560
You

14
00:01:23,959 --> 00:01:25,200
From this day on

15
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:27,159
You will follow me everywhere

16
00:01:27,439 --> 00:01:28,439
As my servant

17
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:30,760
Don't even think about playing tricks

18
00:01:32,359 --> 00:01:33,400
Leaving him in the tent

19
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,079
Might not be appropriate

20
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:36,239
Guarding the Qixi Star Diagram is my duty

21
00:01:36,239 --> 00:01:37,079
What's inappropriate about it?

22
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:38,760
You know me

23
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,000
Once I've made a decision

24
00:01:40,239 --> 00:01:41,120
I never change it

25
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:54,200
Sigh

26
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:56,879
You seem like an educated person

27
00:01:57,400 --> 00:01:58,799
Why are you so clumsy?

28
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,280
Who says an educated person

29
00:02:00,280 --> 00:02:01,319
Must know how to grind ink?

30
00:02:01,560 --> 00:02:02,040
Let me do it

31
00:02:02,239 --> 00:02:02,719
No need

32
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:03,920
Let him do it

33
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,560
I don't keep idlers in my tent

34
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:07,879
Even with a token, it's no exception

35
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,360
Grinding ink is done in two ways

36
00:02:18,319 --> 00:02:19,199
The first way is

37
00:02:19,560 --> 00:02:20,280
Push

38
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:21,439
and pull

39
00:02:22,159 --> 00:02:22,759
Back and forth

40
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,240
This is called grinding

41
00:02:25,199 --> 00:02:26,000
The second way

42
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:27,680
Is to move in circles

43
00:02:28,159 --> 00:02:29,319
This is called rubbing

44
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:34,919
However

45
00:02:35,280 --> 00:02:37,000
The technique of applying the right amount of force in grinding and rubbing

46
00:02:37,560 --> 00:02:38,639
Is something I still don't fully understand

47
00:02:39,599 --> 00:02:40,599
Why don't you teach me again?

48
00:03:00,919 --> 00:03:01,560
Alright.

49
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,039
Yan Ying.

50
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:07,360
Go handle your other duties.

51
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,520
I'll teach him.

52
00:03:16,919 --> 00:03:17,759
When grinding ink,

53
00:03:19,159 --> 00:03:19,960
you need to be quick

54
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,000
and apply strength.

55
00:03:23,039 --> 00:03:23,319
Your hand...

56
00:03:27,800 --> 00:03:28,759
just like this.

57
00:03:37,840 --> 00:03:39,360
Thank you for the guidance, General Xiao.

58
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,439
I've got the hang of it now.

59
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,639
I shall take my leave.

60
00:03:43,319 --> 00:03:44,560
You can fool Yan Ying,

61
00:03:45,120 --> 00:03:46,000
but not me.

62
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,199
You can fool Yan Ying,

63
00:03:59,639 --> 00:04:00,599
but not me.

64
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:07,919
Come with me.

65
00:04:08,560 --> 00:04:09,120
Yan Ying is looking for you.

66
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:11,759
What does she want?

67
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,360
If you don’t want to go, forget it.

68
00:04:14,199 --> 00:04:14,599
Wait.

69
00:04:15,719 --> 00:04:16,319
I’ll go with you.

70
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,000
Yan Ying isn’t even here.

71
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:32,680
You really are lying to me!

72
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:36,160
I’m not lying to you.

73
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,480
If I told the truth, would you have followed me?

74
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,360
So you know who I am?

75
00:04:43,560 --> 00:04:44,160
What do you think?

76
00:04:44,920 --> 00:04:45,560
I am

77
00:04:45,959 --> 00:04:46,720
the creator.

78
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,240
So this was all part of your plan?

79
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:51,279
Are you referring to

80
00:04:51,959 --> 00:04:53,240
this time-travel?

81
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,399
Or the sorry state you’re in now?

82
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,399
I have many plans,

83
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:58,839
ones you’re not even aware of.

84
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:02,360
You weren’t originally part of them, though.

85
00:05:03,079 --> 00:05:04,120
But now that you’re here,

86
00:05:04,920 --> 00:05:05,720
just accept your fate.

87
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,199
Xiao Chengjing,

88
00:05:09,000 --> 00:05:10,480
no matter what your plan is,

89
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:12,560
Yan Ying will never love you.

90
00:05:15,720 --> 00:05:16,240
Xu Chi,

91
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,040
you’re always so confident.

92
00:05:19,879 --> 00:05:21,680
Just because you're our creator

93
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:24,639
doesn't mean you can manipulate others' destinies at will

94
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:27,639
You wrote that Yan Ying and I grew up together as childhood sweethearts

95
00:05:27,639 --> 00:05:28,879
innocent and carefree

96
00:05:29,319 --> 00:05:30,439
You wrote that we fought side by side

97
00:05:30,439 --> 00:05:31,399
through life and death

98
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,920
You wrote that I betrayed Yan Ying out of ambition and desire

99
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,560
Fine

100
00:05:36,560 --> 00:05:38,600
Then I can also use ambition and desire

101
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:39,120
to take Yan Ying back

102
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:43,399
You gave Yan Ying a chance to rewrite her fate

103
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,240
I don't need that

104
00:05:45,759 --> 00:05:47,160
All I want is your death

105
00:05:47,759 --> 00:05:48,800
Once you're dead

106
00:05:49,600 --> 00:05:51,120
everything will be over

107
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,560
You're wrong

108
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:56,759
Xiao Chengjing

109
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,439
The chance for Yan Ying to change her destiny

110
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:00,439
wasn't granted by me

111
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,800
It was something she fought for herself

112
00:06:03,920 --> 00:06:04,720
The future she wanted

113
00:06:04,720 --> 00:06:05,759
The love she desired

114
00:06:06,439 --> 00:06:08,279
Everything was the result of her own choices

115
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,560
But she chose me

116
00:06:12,319 --> 00:06:13,439
not you

117
00:06:18,560 --> 00:06:20,079
You and her belong to different worlds

118
00:06:21,079 --> 00:06:22,079
How could there possibly be an ending

119
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:25,480
Xu Chi

120
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,160
You rewrote the ending

121
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,800
binding my fate with Yan Ying's

122
00:06:33,800 --> 00:06:35,399
so I should be with her

123
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,000
As for you

124
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,000
you can die here

125
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,079
You lied to me

126
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,160
You never lost your memory

127
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:52,959
Didn't you lie to me too?

128
00:06:53,399 --> 00:06:54,199
Stealing the astrological chart

129
00:06:54,199 --> 00:06:55,199
and framing Xu Chi

130
00:06:56,920 --> 00:06:58,639
I found this in your tent just now

131
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,560
So that's how it is

132
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:02,920
Luring the tiger out of the mountain

133
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,360
turning the tables

134
00:07:04,959 --> 00:07:05,360
So

135
00:07:05,360 --> 00:07:07,720
from beginning to end, you two were conspiring against me

136
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:09,560
Xiao Chengjing

137
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:11,519
We trust each other

138
00:07:11,639 --> 00:07:12,720
more than you could possibly imagine

139
00:07:26,519 --> 00:07:27,639
I gave you a chance.

140
00:07:28,439 --> 00:07:29,600
As long as you didn't touch Xu Chi,

141
00:07:30,040 --> 00:07:32,040
we wouldn't have ended up like this.

142
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:34,560
Why?

143
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,040
Why did you choose him in the end?

144
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,920
We belong to the same world.

145
00:07:41,959 --> 00:07:43,439
Have you forgotten who you are?

146
00:07:44,639 --> 00:07:46,000
Who I am doesn't matter.

147
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:47,879
What matters is,

148
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,240
who I love.

149
00:08:02,399 --> 00:08:02,680
Fine.

150
00:08:06,959 --> 00:08:08,399
Then let's go to hell together.

151
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:17,399
Qixi Star Chart.
